00:00:57.190 --> 00:01:00.050
And so here, we have a source--

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:03.070
a charge which is moving
with a velocity V.

00:01:03.070 --> 00:01:06.610
And moving charges, or currents,
create magnetic fields.

00:01:06.610 --> 00:01:09.910
You can use your right-hand
and see particles are

00:01:09.910 --> 00:01:11.470
moving in this direction here.

00:01:11.470 --> 00:01:14.980
