00:04:29.550 --> 00:04:33.090
For the new charge
density, we simply

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:37.070
have to multiply
the current density.

00:04:37.070 --> 00:04:41.220
For the current density, we
have to multiply the charge

00:04:41.220 --> 00:04:43.210
